sources.title: Jeannie (restored, colorized) (1941, drama, imdb score: 7.1)
sources.description: Jeannie (also known as Girl in Distress ) is a 1941 British romantic comedy film directed by Harold French and starring Barbara Mullen , Michael Redgrave , and Albert Lieven . The film's sets were designed by Duncan Sutherland . Based on a play of the same name by Aim√©e Stuart , it was loosely remade in 1957 as Let's Be Happy .
